        <h1 style="text-align:center; font-size:75; display: inline-block" class="font-weight-bold">A House</h1>
        <h2 style="text-align:center; display: inline-block; font-size: 22px;" > - The Dry Fruit Store</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 15px;">Nuts and dried fruits are a great food to have at hand. They are incredibly good for us and are a great source of protein for those following a plant-based, vegan or vegetarian diet. They provide a unique flavor to many meals helping us whip up a delicious healthy treat in no time. So with that in mind, read on to see how to keep those healthy nibbles fresher for longer.As mentioned, nuts and dried fruits are a great option to have around the home. They provide us with many essential nutrients including fiber, unsaturated fats, vegetable protein, vitamins and minerals. Nuts and dried fruits also make a great healthy snack, they can be enjoyed both in sweet and savory meals plus, they’re a great food to take with you if you need to keep your energy levels up when you’re on the go.</p>
        <br>
        
        <h3>Stock Details</h3>

        <div class="card-body table-responsive p-0" style="background:  wheat; height: 400px;">
            <table class="table table-striped table-head-fixed text-nowrap">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 20%" >Product ID</th>
                    <th style="width: 20%" >Product Name</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%" >Cost Price</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%" >Selling Price</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%" >Stock Available</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%" > </th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% for(var i=0;i<data.length;i++){ %>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= data[i].product_id %></td>
                        <td><%= data[i].product_name %></td>
                        <td><%= data[i].cost_price %></td>
                        <td><%= data[i].selling_price %></td>
                        <td>
                            <div class="progress progress-xs">
                              <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" style="width:20%"></div>
                            </div>
                            <small><%= data[i].stock_available %></small>
                        </td>
                        <td class="project-actions text-right">
                            <a class="btn btn-info btn-sm" href="/update"><i class="fas fa-pencil-alt"></i>Edit</a>
                            <a class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" href="/delete" ><i class="fas fa-trash"></i>Delete</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                <% } %>
            </tbody>
            </table>
